Author: shiveryourselfskinny
Text: Not only does small frequent meals help keep you energized at all times, it's easier for me to eat small amounts of calories and safe foods. Eating small meals frequently is super good for concentration as well. Plus, it increases your metabolism, so you're more likely to break a plateau.
